veinreport
  • Reference
  • News

Report Traffic functions.

report_traffic runs traffic functions.

report_traffic(net = "network/net.rds", width = 1/102)

Arguments

net

path to net.rds
width

Numeric; Widht if cell grid.

Value

a list

Examples

{
vein::inventory(file.path(tempdir()))
source(paste0(file.path(tempdir(), "main.R")))
lot <- report_traffic()
names(lot)
lot
}
